<i>noun</i>: 합승 [합씅] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>합승 [합씅]</dt><br>
<dd>1. carpooling</dd><br>
<dd>자동차 등에 여럿이 함께 탐.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of sharing a car, etc. with other people.</dd><br>
<dd>2. taxi sharing</dd><br>
<dd>다른 승객이 있는 택시를 함께 탐.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of sharing a taxi with another passenger.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>